  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bc1\u00a0- \u0bae\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Government's lack of attention is worrisome - Maithiri",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Russian government has pointed out that the way Sri Lanka acted in the Aeroflot plane issue was wrong.",
        "Former President Maithripala Sirisena mentioned in the House that although the issues mentioned in the reply letter sent by Russia can be implemented, it is worrying that the government is not paying attention to it.",
        "He mentioned the above while presenting a special statement when the Parliament met on Monday (04) under the chairmanship of the Speaker.",
        "He questioned the Education Minister whether any steps have been taken regarding the promotion of air service between Russia and Sri Lanka or whether the imposed ban is still in force.",
        "Responding to the question posed by the former President, Education Minister Sushil Premajayantha said that the minister responsible for this matter is aware of the issues, but I have received the information through legal channels.",
        "He said that on the instructions of the Solicitor General of the Legislature Department, it is expected to hold a discussion at the company level to resolve the issues.",
        "I have sent a letter to the President of Russia regarding the deal with Russia and suspension of air services. After 3 days of sending the letter I received the reply letter.",
        "I sent the reply letter sent by the Russian President to President Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "3 things which can be done by the Government of Sri Lanka are mentioned in the reply letter. If they are implemented, we will be able to resume transactions and air services.",
        "In the reply letter, it was wrong for the Sri Lankan government to go to court on the issue with Aeroflot and the Irish company. Firstly, it is stated that the issue can be resolved through diplomatic level negotiations between the two countries, and secondly, a firm assurance should be given that such activities will not take place in the future.",
        "Fuel and essential commodities that are in short supply in Sri Lanka can be sourced from Russia.",
        "Russia does not negotiate for goods and services on a government basis. Negotiations will be conducted under an institutional framework.",
        "In order to get the fuel, the Sri Lankan Petroleum Corporation has to negotiate with the Russian Fuel Company.",
        "We have to negotiate with the Russian company for the goods we need. A third stated that negotiations at the government and embassy level were unnecessary.",
        "He said that although the three issues mentioned in the reply letter sent by the Russian government could be implemented, it is a matter of concern that the government has not implemented them."
      ],
